                    <div class=\"step-wrapper pb-3\">\n                        <h3 class=\"step d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\" data-app-selector=\".step\" mbr-class=\"{'m-auto': alignNumber == '2', 'ml-auto': alignNumber == '3'}\">\n                            6\n                        </h3>\n                    </div>          \n                    <div class=\"step-text-content align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"mbr-step-title pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-step-title\" mbr-if=\"showStepTitle\">\n                            Deployment\n                        </h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-step-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-step-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nam erat libero, bibendum in libero tempor, luctus volutpat ligula.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"card col-12\" mbr-if=\"stepsAmount > 6\" mbr-class=\"{'separline': stepsAmount > '7' || alignNumber == '2', 'last-child': stepsAmount == '7', 'col-md-6': stepsAmount < 9, 'col-md-4': stepsAmount > 8}\">\n                <div class=\"step-element\">\n                    <div class=\"step-wrapper pb-3\">\n                        <h3 class=\"step d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\" data-app-selector=\".step\" mbr-class=\"{'m-auto': alignNumber == '2', 'ml-auto': alignNumber == '3'}\">\n                            7\n                        </h3>\n                    </div>          \n                    <div class=\"step-text-content align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"mbr-step-title pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-step-title\" mbr-if=\"showStepTitle\">\n                            Deployment\n                        </h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-step-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-step-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nam erat libero, bibendum in libero tempor, luctus volutpat ligula.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"card col-12\" mbr-if=\"stepsAmount > 7\" mbr-class=\"{'separline': stepsAmount > '8' || alignNumber == '2', 'last-child': stepsAmount == '8', 'col-md-6': stepsAmount < 9, 'col-md-4': stepsAmount > 8}\">\n                <div class=\"step-element\">\n                    <div class=\"step-wrapper pb-3\">\n                        <h3 class=\"step d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\" data-app-selector=\".step\" mbr-class=\"{'m-auto': alignNumber == '2', 'ml-auto': alignNumber == '3'}\">\n                            8\n                        </h3>\n                    </div>          \n                    <div class=\"step-text-content align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"mbr-step-title pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-step-title\" mbr-if=\"showStepTitle\">\n                            Deployment\n                        </h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-step-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-step-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nam erat libero, bibendum in libero tempor, luctus volutpat ligula.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"card col-md-4 col-12\" mbr-if=\"stepsAmount > 8\" mbr-class=\"{'separline': alignNumber == '2'}\">\n                <div class=\"step-element\">\n                    <div class=\"step-wrapper pb-3\">\n                        <h3 class=\"step d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center\" data-app-selector=\".step\" mbr-class=\"{'m-auto': alignNumber == '2', 'ml-auto': alignNumber == '3'}\">\n                            9\n                        </h3>\n                    </div>          \n                    <div class=\"step-text-content align-center\">\n                        <h4 class=\"mbr-step-title pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-step-title\" mbr-if=\"showStepTitle\">\n                            Deployment\n                        </h4>\n                        <p class=\"mbr-step-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-step-text\">\n                            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Nam erat libero, bibendum in libero tempor, luctus volutpat ligula.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
